WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: cKBV_VHao_Q

NOTE Language: en

00:00:10.241 --> 00:00:16.354
I'm very happy to see you all in such a beautiful dresses,

00:00:16.555 --> 00:00:24.180
and also in a good mood to get married.

00:00:27.865 --> 00:00:33.977
You must keep up your attitude - all right

00:00:34.178 --> 00:00:37.005
You should be happy people,

00:00:37.206 --> 00:00:42.068
and try to keep your husbands also happy.

00:00:42.269 --> 00:00:48.427
Your happiness can create happiness for the children.

00:00:48.628 --> 00:00:51.159
Now one thing I want to warn you:

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:54.253
not to tell your husband about anything

00:00:54.454 --> 00:00:58.261
which was wrong in your past life. That's not to be done,

00:00:58.462 --> 00:01:01.605
there's no need, because you are now Sahaja Yogis.

00:01:01.806 --> 00:01:05.222
You are changed people and whatever has happened has happened,

00:01:05.423 --> 00:01:09.277
you need not talk about it or tell him anything about it,

00:01:09.478 --> 00:01:12.769
but talk of the future and the present - all right?

00:01:12.970 --> 00:01:14.839
So, be sensible!

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:19.886
It's your sensibility which is going to make a happy married life.

00:01:20.087 --> 00:01:22.253
If you become insensible,

00:01:22.454 --> 00:01:26.464
there's no wisdom, then marriages will fail.

00:01:26.665 --> 00:01:31.027
Some girls, I've seen, dominate their husbands too much.

00:01:31.228 --> 00:01:33.105
There is no need to dominate.

00:01:33.306 --> 00:01:37.355
If you love the husband that's how the domination is,

00:01:37.556 --> 00:01:41.683
is the best way is to love your husband, look after him,

00:01:41.884 --> 00:01:47.042
do whatever is needed, because no use showing off

00:01:47.243 --> 00:01:53.011
that you are from a better society or a better culture

00:01:53.212 --> 00:01:57.784
or a better family background.

00:01:57.985 --> 00:02:02.854
 It's only you who can show that you are really a good person

00:02:03.055 --> 00:02:05.401
and your goodness will win him over.

00:02:05.602 --> 00:02:09.268
So it's only the wife who makes or spoils the marriage.

00:02:09.469 --> 00:02:12.362
And I have to tell you very frankly

00:02:12.563 --> 00:02:17.018
that if you still have some doubts about your marriage

00:02:17.219 --> 00:02:20.862
or if you are still thinking this was not a good match

00:02:21.063 --> 00:02:23.651
you should withdraw now. And later on

00:02:23.852 --> 00:02:26.924
you should not go on finding faults with your husband.

00:02:27.125 --> 00:02:30.510
See, men are men and women are women.

00:02:30.711 --> 00:02:35.431
Men cannot be women but, you can make them understand

00:02:35.632 --> 00:02:40.494
that women are to be respected. All right, and how -

00:02:40.695 --> 00:02:43.322
that you will have to see by your behaviour.

00:02:43.523 --> 00:02:46.838
 If your behaviour is good, they'll respect you.

00:02:47.039 --> 00:02:49.580
But if your behaviour is childish

00:02:49.781 --> 00:02:52.283
or if your behaviour is aggressive,

00:02:52.484 --> 00:02:55.533
no man can appreciate a woman who is aggressive

00:02:55.734 --> 00:02:58.150
and so you should not be aggressive.

00:02:58.351 --> 00:03:02.189
Whatever he says you should agree and listen to him.

00:03:02.390 --> 00:03:04.720
Fundamental things of course is there,

00:03:04.921 --> 00:03:07.009
but otherwise for small, small things,

00:03:07.210 --> 00:03:09.618
you should not try to dominate your husband.

00:03:09.819 --> 00:03:13.712
It's not a sign of a Sahaja Yogini. Sahaja Yogini has to -

00:03:13.913 --> 00:03:17.220
with love and understanding and wisdom -

00:03:17.421 --> 00:03:21.822
has to win over the husband and not by domination.

00:03:22.023 --> 00:03:24.486
This is one thing we should understand

00:03:24.687 --> 00:03:29.564
that many marriages are broken because of domination.

00:03:29.765 --> 00:03:34.947
Second thing is, you're naturally attached to your parents,

00:03:35.148 --> 00:03:38.174
attached to your family, attached to your country.

00:03:38.375 --> 00:03:43.276
But now, forget it! Be attached to your husband's family,

00:03:43.477 --> 00:03:46.518
husband and things around.

00:03:46.719 --> 00:03:48.768
Because if you are attached to your family,

00:03:48.969 --> 00:03:51.791
you'll still spoil the relationship.

00:03:51.992 --> 00:03:56.166
I've known many couples being broken because of this.

00:03:56.367 --> 00:03:59.689
There was a girl who was very much worried about her father,

00:03:59.890 --> 00:04:01.361
because he'd lost the business

00:04:01.562 --> 00:04:04.142
and she made the whole life miserable.

00:04:04.343 --> 00:04:06.806
So the husband disappeared

00:04:07.007 --> 00:04:09.181
and he wanted to do something else

00:04:09.382 --> 00:04:12.525
and she was left in the lurch and she had to go to her father

00:04:12.726 --> 00:04:17.813
and then she realized how difficult it is to live in father's house.

00:04:18.014 --> 00:04:22.650
So, it's your house, it's your home, it's your husband.

00:04:22.851 --> 00:04:27.166
All right, you don't have to sort of go on searching

00:04:27.367 --> 00:04:31.658
another person or another woman who will help you.

00:04:31.859 --> 00:04:35.064
 It's you who can help yourself.  All right?

00:04:35.265 --> 00:04:38.994
because now we have very bad experiences of some girls

00:04:39.195 --> 00:04:40.778
who have left their husband

00:04:40.979 --> 00:04:45.255
and come away to their families with their children.

00:04:45.456 --> 00:04:50.247
Is the family going to look after them all their lives?

00:04:50.448 --> 00:04:52.755
Who is going to look after them?

00:04:52.956 --> 00:04:56.793
So use your brain and don't try to show off

00:04:56.994 --> 00:05:00.285
that you are something superior or something higher

00:05:00.486 --> 00:05:02.808
or you're something more.

00:05:03.009 --> 00:05:05.449
Say something you should be humble.

00:05:05.650 --> 00:05:08.254
The humble you are the better it is.

00:05:08.455 --> 00:05:12.348
Otherwise arrogance doesn't behove you. She doesn't look nice,

00:05:12.549 --> 00:05:15.848
she looks like a horse sometimes and looks like -

00:05:16.049 --> 00:05:20.911
I don't know like what. So it is better to be humble

00:05:21.112 --> 00:05:25.403
and to be kind and to be nice and to prove that

00:05:25.604 --> 00:05:32.588
you are a good natured person. All right?

00:05:34.079 --> 00:05:38.753
Second thing I have to tell you, because you are from the West.

00:05:38.954 --> 00:05:41.784
So western women are very much money-oriented,

00:05:41.985 --> 00:05:45.050
even Indians have become like that. They want a car,

00:05:45.251 --> 00:05:49.378
they want a house, they want this, they want that.

00:05:49.579 --> 00:05:53.855
You shouldn't want anything.

00:05:54.056 --> 00:05:57.214
You are going to supply to your husband, to your family.

00:05:57.415 --> 00:06:00.612
You don't need anything.

00:06:00.813 --> 00:06:05.518
That's your beauty, that's your decoration that will beautify you.

00:06:05.719 --> 00:06:09.448
But if you go on hankering after "I want this, I want that"

00:06:09.649 --> 00:06:13.768
there's no end to it. Especially with western mind,

00:06:13.969 --> 00:06:17.807
they are very money-oriented and have created such problems

00:06:18.008 --> 00:06:20.385
that I don't know what to say to them.

00:06:20.586 --> 00:06:23.674
So, second thing is that you should not be money-oriented,

00:06:23.875 --> 00:06:25.760
but you should be love-oriented.

00:06:25.961 --> 00:06:30.432
Express your love by different things. By making good food,

00:06:30.633 --> 00:06:33.495
by making a good bed for your husband,

00:06:33.696 --> 00:06:37.839
for organizing the house, keeping everything nice.

00:06:38.040 --> 00:06:42.206
Because if the housewife is untidy the house will remain untidy.

00:06:42.407 --> 00:06:45.073
It's not the job of the husband to look after the house.

00:06:45.274 --> 00:06:49.393
You'll enjoy a very beautiful house and a very beautiful room,

00:06:49.594 --> 00:06:52.940
 if you keep it properly. So you should enjoy all that.

00:06:53.141 --> 00:06:57.096
Enjoy doing everything for the family. Especially for your husband.

00:06:57.297 --> 00:07:01.487
Little, little things can - you see - give him pleasure and happiness.

00:07:01.688 --> 00:07:04.175
Because he's so tired working in the office.

00:07:04.376 --> 00:07:07.698
Coming home so tired and then you get after that person,

00:07:07.899 --> 00:07:09.698
is very wrong.

00:07:09.899 --> 00:07:14.815
So you must change that attitude that we don't want anything.

00:07:15.016 --> 00:07:17.456
You have everything, you are Sahaja Yogis,

00:07:17.657 --> 00:07:20.667
you are absolutely satisfied.

00:07:20.868 --> 00:07:24.457
But if you go on demanding then going to be very difficult

00:07:24.658 --> 00:07:26.105
I can tell you this much.

00:07:26.306 --> 00:07:29.230
I've had very, very bad experiences of some girls.

00:07:29.431 --> 00:07:33.730
Say from Austria recently, three girls went away back to Austria,

00:07:33.931 --> 00:07:39.035
it's shameful. Is there anybody from Austria here?

00:07:39.236 --> 00:07:42.027
No. Thank God!

00:07:42.228 --> 00:07:47.519
You are from Austria? Wa, Wa! Now, be careful!

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:51.441
You see these, the three girls have come back with the children.

00:07:51.642 --> 00:07:54.771
And the husband is so dominated that he has to go

00:07:54.972 --> 00:07:57.513
to the father's house every Saturday, Sunday.

00:07:57.714 --> 00:08:02.112
He's spending all that money in going down.

00:08:02.378 --> 00:08:06.911
That doesn't show any wisdom. You see, the housewife,

00:08:07.112 --> 00:08:11.333
not only makes the family grow,

00:08:11.534 --> 00:08:14.708
but bring good name and understanding.

00:08:14.909 --> 00:08:18.966
There's nothing to suffer much, but understanding is required, you see?

00:08:19.167 --> 00:08:23.599
Supposing, if you are wise and if something happens,

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:28.880
take a very wise attitude, balanced attitude, responsible attitude.

00:08:29.081 --> 00:08:31.927
Wife has to be much more responsible than man

00:08:32.128 --> 00:08:35.427
as far as the family is concerned, children are concerned.

00:08:35.628 --> 00:08:37.865
But if you are a hot tempered woman,

00:08:38.066 --> 00:08:40.037
God save you and save your husband.

00:08:40.238 --> 00:08:44.092
So, hot temper is not suitable at all for any woman.

00:08:44.293 --> 00:08:48.436
If you are hot tempered you'll start looking old very soon.

00:08:48.637 --> 00:08:51.772
Very soon you will start looking old, and if you have ego,

00:08:51.973 --> 00:08:55.811
if you think too much of yourself also same thing will happen.

00:08:56.012 --> 00:08:59.702
So, best thing is to behave like a little girl

00:08:59.903 --> 00:09:02.788
who has come to husband's house to love him,

00:09:02.989 --> 00:09:05.913
to look after him and to mother him.

00:09:06.114 --> 00:09:09.663
You have to think that you are his mother and he -

00:09:09.864 --> 00:09:12.757
sometimes they are foolish according to your judgement -

00:09:12.958 --> 00:09:17.179
doesn't matter. So, look after them just like your baby

00:09:17.380 --> 00:09:21.015
and be nice and sweet to them. All right?

00:09:21.216 --> 00:09:26.851
And none of your family people are more important than your husband.

00:09:27.052 --> 00:09:28.351
That is very important.

00:09:28.552 --> 00:09:32.007
For you now the most important thing your husband.

00:09:32.208 --> 00:09:34.343
This is a Sahaja style of marriage.

00:09:34.544 --> 00:09:37.570
And you can have other marriages, you can have ten marriages -

00:09:37.771 --> 00:09:41.586
that's different, not in Sahaja Yoga. And once you are divorced

00:09:41.787 --> 00:09:45.375
then we don't marry you. We have given up, we tried that.

00:09:45.576 --> 00:09:47.016
Now we don't do that.

00:09:47.217 --> 00:09:50.633
Because it becomes a habit of divorcing your husband.

00:09:50.834 --> 00:09:54.000
Once you are married you should be all married

00:09:54.201 --> 00:09:57.875
and if you want to divorce then know before this thing

00:09:58.076 --> 00:10:00.531
that we'll have nothing to do with you.

00:10:00.732 --> 00:10:03.961
And you'll be thrown away from Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:04.162 --> 00:10:09.766
We want to have very good marriages and very good children.

00:10:09.967 --> 00:10:14.594
Also the progeny, the future of children will be very good,

00:10:14.795 --> 00:10:21.875
if you are sensible, wise, good and kind mothers.

00:10:22.076 --> 00:10:25.656
I've told you sufficiently. I hope you understand that

00:10:25.857 --> 00:10:27.554
you are marrying in Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:27.755 --> 00:10:31.593
And you have to keep the prestige of Sahaja Yoga, all right?

00:10:31.794 --> 00:10:35.038
You all promise that?

00:10:35.239 --> 00:10:39.067
May God bless you!
